Applications:
chkalloc	- check for memory leaks in a program that uses MALLOC,
		  CALLOC, REALLOC, and FREE. See alloc (3).
tmexec		- spawn a sub-process. KILL it after a set time.
allocfvi	- print pointers and values of a multi-dimensional array.

Library functions:
alloc		- allocators with optional diagnostics.
alloc2f		- allocate a two dimensional array of floats
alloc3f		- allocate a three dimensional array of floats
alloc4f		- allocate a four dimensional array of floats
dyn_alloc	- concatenate data, allocating more memory if necessary.
err_msg		- accumulate and print error messages.
hash		- simple hash table
str		- dynamic strings
